We run a Git pre-commit hook, which runs our LintRoller config. This way we can't commit bad code.
  - http://www.akawebdesign.com/2012/12/12/using-lintroller-with-a-git-pre-commit-hook/

-----

If you're on Mac/Linux, run "install.sh" on your local machine.

If you're on Windows, run "install.bat" on your local machine.